Package: eva-bot
Architecture: amd64
Version: 0.3.12-1
Maintainer: Andreas Mueller <amu@gnoppix.com>
Description: Eva Reflector Bot - Automated echo bot for testing
 Eva Reflector Bot is a headless echo client that reflects messages
 back to senders. Useful for latency testing and protocol verification.
 .
 Features:
  - Echo messages with 🤖 [Reflector Echo]: prefix
  - TTL inheritance from incoming messages
  - E2E read receipts (Double Check)
  - Loop prevention to avoid infinite echo loops
  - Zero-footprint in-memory storage
Depends: libssl3
Section: net
Priority: optional